title: NFL ATL: Super Bowl liabilities, headlines
itunes:title: NFL ATL: Super Bowl liabilities, headlines
description:
A room full of heroes -- Dan Hanzus, Gregg Rosenthal and Marc Sessler -- preview potential weak spots for the Denver Broncos and Seattle Seahawks in Super Bowl XLVIII, patch in Kevin Patra from Honolulu to preview the first-ever Pro Bowl Draft and catch up with Chris Wesseling, who makes his case for why this year’s title game is so spectacular.  Join the conversation on Twitter: @NFL_ATL or #NFLATL.

Learn more about your ad-choices at https://www.iheartpodcastnetwork.com
